    "body": "@ctiller and I have discussed this a few times and I think the current working forecast is \"Python 2 is ending; one day we will decide that we have to convert testing and tools scripts to Python 3 and on that day we'll do it all at once\".\r\n\r\nNo need to leave this open; I am strongly _looking forward_ to never seeing Python 2 again but I _opine_ that switching our scripts can wait another... eighteen months? Twenty-four would be pushing it."
